            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#linikD" start="386.641" end="x">They tried . . . The planes were German, they tried to bomb us, bomb us along the way. This [unintelligible] was damaged slightly . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
