                <span class="">Dina Linik</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#linikD" start="393.178" end="x">. . . after that, a strong, six-degree storm began. The storm was tossing the ship like a toy. A few times, we thought that we were going to die. Various . . . confined space, this emotional stress . . . made . . . many people . . . many people died on this ship.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
